snippet.title: WRITHE Nintendo Switch announcement trailer (OFFICIAL)
snippet.description:
Grab your guns and paint the floor with GRUBJUICE!

WRITHE transports you to an alternate ’70s Thailand, where an endless horde of mutant sago worms terrorise the good people of Bangkok. Suit up and lock ‘n’ load- it’s your duty as an exterminator to hold back this wriggling tide to the last breath.

WRITHE will be exclusively available for pre-order on the Nintendo Switch eShop from December 28th 2020, you can view the store page here: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/WRITHE-1896526.html





You can also find out more about WRITHE and Mission Ctrl Studios below:

Mission Ctrl Studios: https://www.mission-ctrl.co.uk

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MissionCtrlHQ

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/MissionCtrlHQ

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MissionCtrlHQ
